UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 542
1 A RESOLUTION confirming the reappointment of Kathryn Thomas to the Board
2 of Claims.
3 WHEREAS, on May 15, 2025, in accordance with KRS 49.020 and by virtue of
4 Executive Order 2025-300, Governor Andy Beshear reappointed Kathryn Thomas to the
5 Board of Claims for a term expiring June 29, 2029; and
6 WHEREAS, the reappointment is subject to Senate confirmation; and
7 WHEREAS, Kathryn Thomas has been determined to meet the requirements of
8 KRS 49.020;
9 NOW, THEREFORE,
10 Be it resolved by the Senate of the General Assembly of the Commonwealth of
11 Kentucky:
12 Section 1. The Senate hereby confirms the reappointment of Kathryn Thomas to
13 the Board of Claims.
14 Section 2. The Clerk of the Senate shall forward a copy of this Resolution and
15 notification of its adoption to Kathryn Thomas of Glasgow, Barren County, Kentucky,
16 and to Governor Andy Beshear, 703 Capital Avenue, Room 133, Frankfort, Kentucky
17 40601.
